'''screenshot_format''' is a variable of Openttd.cfg file:

The format to use when taking [[en/screenshot]]s. This is a client-setting only.

==Use==

"BMP" is the default setting.  You may change this setting through the [[en/game options window]] or [[en/openttd.cfg]] with the following syntax:

<pre>
[misc]
screenshot_format = <Valid options>
</pre>

'''Valid options:''' [ <empty> | bmp | png | pcx ]

'''Default:''' <empty>

If an invalid setting is entered, then it will revert to the default.

